OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be mostly dry
OL,6,Fwith some sunny intervals. Variable
OL,7,Famounts of cloud this afternoon with
OL,8,Fsunny intervals and just a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Freshening southwesterly
OL,10,Fbreeze this afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. The rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will be largely dry with clear
OL,15,Fspells, a few light showers in the
OL,16,Fnorth and west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
