OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and a few bright
OL,7,Fspells. The odd light shower in
OL,8,Fnorthwest. Outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,9,Fnortheast in the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FScattered slow moving showers on
OL,13,FTuesday, occasionally heavy. Mainly
OL,14,Fdry on Wednesday, a little light rain
OL,15,Flikely later. A few showers at first
OL,16,Fon Thursday, otherwise dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
